Omoyemi Akerele bụ onye guzobere na onye isi nchịkwa nke Style House Files, ụlọ ọrụ mmepe azụmahịa ejiji nke na-elekwasị anya na ụlọ ọrụ ejiji nke Naijiria na Afrịka
Ọ malitere Lagos Fashion and Design Week na ụlọ ọrụ mmepe okike ya na-enye ngalaba mmepụta ejiji dị iche iche n'Afrịka ohere igosi na Pitti Immagine na Italy na Lagos Fashion and Design Week.
Omoyemi gara mahadum Lagos ebe o nwetara nzere bachelọ na iwu
Ọ gakwara na Mahadum Warwick ebe ọ nwetara nzere masta na Iwu akụnụba mba ụwa
Ọ rụrụ ọrụ na Olaniwun Ajayi & Co ụlọ ọrụ iwu Naijiria site na 2000 ruo 2003 tupu ọ bụrụ onye nrụpụta ejiji
Ọ bụ onye nchịkọta akụkọ ejiji maka akwụkwọ akụkọ ndụ a na-akpọ True Love
